{"tid":2290361,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"這算是情侶物品吧！因同款太多而被質疑熱戀的NCT泰容和RED VELVET Yeri","createTime":"2020-11-18T03:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T03:33:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a2eae194ea3919d6f998ac3112e7bfd74a1b0e5","tid":2290361,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_9209218361a17f514605ccc687e343e4/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-17/131693-885091.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_9209218361a17f514605ccc687e343e4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-17%2F131693-885091.png&h=81ddb154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSM娛樂又出了一對社內CP？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11月8日，韓網PANN社區一個題為「這是情侶物品沒錯吧」的貼文引發了廣大網民的關注，閱讀量有23萬之多和上百條留言。 PO主貼出多張照片，指出Red Velvet的老么Yeri和NCT的隊長泰容有不少相同物品，有次猜測兩人是在談戀愛。<br />\n<br />\n1. 兩人佩戴過同款針織帽<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_803dd74c5cc674061770ceec0b66025a/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-17/131693-885092.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_803dd74c5cc674061770ceec0b66025a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-17%2F131693-885092.jpeg&h=874b0872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 兩人都有這款兔子玩偶<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_22195160e01d9a56cc0ed22c6b1041b5/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-17/131693-885093.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_22195160e01d9a56cc0ed22c6b1041b5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-17%2F131693-885093.jpeg&h=f96b9526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_db5193042565f7ac8fdb85105eea536f/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-17/131693-885094.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_db5193042565f7ac8fdb85105eea536f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-17%2F131693-885094.jpeg&h=dabb1ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 兩人曾使用過同款B牌小熊掛件<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c0f72da4bcbef28bc580503f0a93c0c0/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-17/131693-885095.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c0f72da4bcbef28bc580503f0a93c0c0%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-17%2F131693-885095.jpeg&h=a78fb382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網友同意PO主的猜測，留言表示：「1、2樣就算了，三個以上重合的話確實....」、「SM喜歡本來就社內戀愛啊」、「對，就是在談戀愛吧」。<br />\n<br />\n不過也有知情網友反駁PO主，指出上述猜測毫無根據，稱：「帽子是品牌方讚助的，並非Yeri自己買的。 兔子玩偶是泰容自己的，因為經常腰疼，而用來墊腰的。 Yeri的兔子則是錄音室的裝飾品，其實是錄音室PD的。 最後小熊掛件是非常出名的搭配單品，NCT其他人也收到了同樣的禮物，Yeri、Heize、太妍也有。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_7b4d91c6dfd11690b9b839f53828bcf8/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-17/131693-885096.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_7b4d91c6dfd11690b9b839f53828bcf8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-17%2F131693-885096.png&h=2d9111fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實這已經不是Yeri和泰容第一次爆出戀愛出爆門，早在2年前傳過，當時網友甚至列舉了7大疑點，包括：用相同的杯子蛋糕擺出相似的POSE拍照、兩人不約而同提到想成為消防員、擁有同款護照夾等等。 其中最關鍵的證據，便是Yeri的手機桌面，被指出「就是泰容的照片」。 對於當時的爆料，大部份粉絲都不以為然，吐槽是爆料人想太多。<br />\n<br />\n「圖：Yeri IG、泰容IG、PANN」"},{"pid":"dc28515867e52c357b9b34876cdb65f7cd6291fa","tid":2290361,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"@<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907335105865312159a2a542fa86cd92e4806c20","tid":2290361,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc28515867e52c357b9b34876cdb65f7cd6291fa","tid":2290361,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"@<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:12:37.000Z","msg":"RV<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aac051752dbb29ef0e6e47c1ca139e97cdc5f09","tid":2290361,"uid":93096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141415181a57423ae63dd6f72eb73374ff9dd046","tid":2290361,"uid":121249,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:24:46.000Z","msg":"rv仲未解散？？"},{"pid":"6c5ddfaca08723021c07939ab16d0bd34cd6121f","tid":2290361,"uid":294121,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"泰容跳舞咁勁<br />\n一定屌到yeri啪啪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0135b94a8bfdc3ac1f5cdf5f079002475d184b","tid":2290361,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"141415181a57423ae63dd6f72eb73374ff9dd046","tid":2290361,"uid":121249,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:24:46.000Z","msg":"rv仲未解散？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:33:39.000Z","msg":"俾老女人累死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}